Package com.btc.redg.runtime.defaultvalues.pluggable

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PluggableDefaultValueProvider
    The interface to be used with the PluggableDefaultValueStrategy.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractDateProvider
    The base class for PluggableDefaultValueProviders providing dates.
    ConditionalProvider
    A PluggableDefaultValueProvider that delegates the value request to a provided PluggableDefaultValueProvider if the table and column match a specified regular expression.
    ConstantStringProvider
    A PluggableDefaultValueProvider that returns a constant string.
    ConstantValueProvider
    A PluggableDefaultValueProvider that provides a constant object for every field with the exact type.
    CurrentDateProvider
    A PluggableDefaultValueProvider always returning the current date.
    CustomConditionalProvider
    A conditional provider that is even more flexible than the ConditionalProvider
    DefaultDefaultValueProvider
    A PluggableDefaultValueProvider returning the default value from a DefaultDefaultValueStrategy.
    IncrementingNumberProvider
    A PluggableDefaultValueProvider that provides incrementing numbers.
    NumberProvider
    A PluggableDefaultValueProvider that is capable of providing numbers.
    PluggableDefaultValueStrategy
    A DefaultValueStrategy that implements a simple plugin system.
    StaticDateProvider
    A PluggableDefaultValueProvider that provides a static date.
    StaticNumberProvider
    A PluggableDefaultValueProvider that provides a static number.
